cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM

The paper discusses neural network-based clustering for transfer learning and image category discovery using deep learning. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and multimedia (cs.MM). However, since the paper focuses on deep learning-based clustering, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories.
